node.text:
Hope you all had an amazing New Year's Eve and are ready to bury a horrible 2020. We start things off in 2021 with a frickin' amazing box + stellar glassware from Mikkeller Baghaven 🥂

Tempted to be a member of the club? There is a couple of seats available right here! Go to @mikkellerwebshop and sign up today!

The Beer Club membership includes the following:
- Between 7 to 11 beers depending on the flow of new arrivals
- Limited stuff (from time to time) that isn't for sale in the webshop otherwise
- All styles of beer - both Mikkeller releases (new and old) but also exclusive brews from our long list of friends
- Access to Beer Club meetups and exclusive events and openings

Which beer from the box will you pop as the first in 2021? 🍾

node.title: 🥂 Mikkeller Beer Club - New Year, New Me Edition 🥂

Happy New Year everyone! 🍾

The craziest (and only?) dance beer project so far! 🕺💃 Mikkeller x People Like Us x Bjarke Østergaard (Brewery Dancer) x Carling Talcott-Steenstra (dancer at the Danish Royal Ballet) x Sebastian Kloborg (choreographer) x Aaron Dessner (music) x Henrik Vibskov (costumes) proudly presents: 🌱 SPONTAN GOES SPONTAN 🌱

A Sour Ale brewed with Bergamot, aged in oak barrels 🍋

WHY SPONTAN GOES SPONTAN?
Bjarke Østergaard is autistic and has ADHD - and is really good at dancing. He was given up by the system and declared “not suitable to work”. Now he’s the World’s first brewery dancer - and he works at People Like Us, doing marketing on a special dance beer series through dancing. Spontan Goes Spontan is a crazy collaboration between various artists and breweries to create a full experience surrounding this beer and share the story of brewery dancer Bjarke. Dance is a universal language. Just like beer. 
LAUNCH PERFORMANCE: Friday, March 6th, at @srbb_festival 2020!

The beer will be available at the festival this weekend and can be purchased at all Mikkeller locations and from the Mikkeller and PLU webshops from the beginning of next week.

Join the #socialrevolutionbybeer!
Secure your tickets for the awesome beer festival to experience the Spontan Goes Spontan launch performance and enjoy crazy amounts of good craft beer! Get them right here: www.srbb.peoplelikeus.dk/tickets/

@peoplelikeusdk is a Danish brewery who, besides brewing craft beer, create jobs for people from socially marginalized groups.
90% of their 60 employees have a diagnosis. @mikkellerbeer are close supporters and business mentors of People Like Us.

Wanna create some wild magic? 🍾⁠
⁠
@mikkellerbaghaven is currently looking for a passionate and experienced wild ale brewer to join the team full time at our facilities on Refshaleøen in Copenhagen, Denmark.

We are looking for a passionated and experienced wild ale brewer, who are well versed in the production and blending of wild fermented beverages 🌿
⁠
𝗜𝗻 𝗼𝗿𝗱𝗲𝗿 𝘁𝗼 𝗯𝗲 𝗰𝗼𝗻𝘀𝗶𝗱𝗲𝗿𝗲𝗱 𝗳𝗼𝗿 𝘁𝗵𝗶𝘀 𝗽𝗼𝘀𝗶𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝘆𝗼𝘂 𝗺𝘂𝘀𝘁:⁠
-Have an incredible passion for producing and blending wild ale⁠
-Have a minimum of 2 year’s experience in a brewery that specializes in producing wild ales and other barrel aged beers, with a track record of direct success in that production⁠
-Have incredible attention to detail⁠
-Be involved in determining blends, and the constant pursuit of improvement and perfection⁠
-Have a current, or able to obtain shortly after employment, a Danish driver’s license⁠
-Have legal right to reside and work in Denmark/ EU⁠
⁠
𝗝𝗼𝗯 𝗥𝗲𝘀𝗽𝗼𝗻𝘀𝗶𝗯𝗶𝗹𝗶𝘁𝗶𝗲𝘀:⁠
-Wort production at our sister brewpub Warpigs, according to our recipes and protocols⁠
-Transportation of wort and other raw materials to and from the Blenderia/Baghaven⁠
-Filling, emptying, cleaning, stacking and preparing oak for aging and fermentation⁠
-Properly transferring beer to make blends.⁠
-Processing fruit⁠
-Cleaning tanks and barrels according to our SOP.⁠
-Packaging/ labeling⁠
-Safely operating a forklift⁠
-Maintain workplace safety while upholding quality standards and standard operating procedures⁠
-Periodically represent and work at festivals and events⁠
-Perform routine preventative maintenance and cleaning of equipment and infrastructure⁠
-In general, maintain extreme cleanliness of the Blenderia/Baghaven⁠
-Work periodic nights and weekends when deemed necessary⁠
⁠
𝗦𝗸𝗶𝗹𝗹𝘀 𝗰𝗼𝗻𝘀𝗶𝗱𝗲𝗿𝗲𝗱 𝗮 𝗽𝗹𝘂𝘀:⁠
-Brewery/winery laboratory practices⁠
-Winery experience⁠
-Fruit fermentation experience⁠
-Fundamental knowledge in microbiology, chemistry, and/ or oenology⁠
⁠
𝗦𝗼𝘂𝗻𝗱𝘀 𝗹𝗶𝗸𝗲 𝘀𝗼𝗺𝗲𝘁𝗵𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗳𝗼𝗿 𝘆𝗼𝘂?⁠
Qualified candidates should submit a CV and cover letter to ehren@mikkeller.dk with “Blender 2021” in the subject line 📬
